{"tid":1802554,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"時機未到，未準備好，希望大家冷靜少少，諗清楚香港需要啲咩？","createTime":"2019-12-29T14:26:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-30T06:03:32.000Z","uid":35699,"like":3,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"2f581a669335fe15d5d6f6a7d37d38c7ded93ec5","tid":1802554,"uid":35699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T14:26:55.000Z","msg":"香港需要自主嗎？需要！<br />\n香港需要民主嗎？需要！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n但係事情有緩急先後，做事要分主次，（某件事A）係香港大部分人嘅共識，（某件事B）係一個好好嘅願景，但未經過廣泛討論，未成氣候，大家應該慢慢講，從長計議！！！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n事件A 你會代入啲咩呢？ <br />\n事件B 你會代入啲咩呢？<br />\n<br />\n1）A= 經濟發展 ，B=普選 ？？<br />\n2）A= 五大訴求， B=香港獨立？？？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果你唔明支持香港獨立嘅人嘅心情，可以試吓將自己代入「1）」嘅情況，真普選唔俾講嘅時候你會點睇？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n就好似依家咁，「香港獨立」堂而皇之，但可惜已成連登禁語，唔俾講，唔俾出現。"},{"pid":"bd9c6daffeaf7e3c7e1d206b4432fb5745a65178","tid":1802554,"uid":35699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T14:28:06.000Z","msg":"連登仔九成唔會聽，我留個名，入集中營前鞭返上嚟"},{"pid":"86d0b01aa0f9ec0d4f938db049e50bd830eb1986","tid":1802554,"uid":292730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T14:28:58.000Z","msg":"借位幫推<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />香港人。帶遮<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n元旦遊行：上次128全香港人都漏左樣好重既野<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1802514\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1802514</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"ab1db5fd1c518acba45e12bdb13815d0db7c49f3","tid":1802554,"uid":174174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T14:30:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n要進步"},{"pid":"1a19d12dbc84fb967703ea5a6c5428542e61cebc","tid":1802554,"uid":305536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T14:32:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>德國聯署有三份  呢家<span style=\"color: red;\">仲有一份未達標</span><br />\n而且差好遠呀<strong><s